– FastAPI for building the REST API;
– Uvicorn as the ASGI server;
– scikit‐learn and pandas for ML;
– joblib for serializing the model;
– nltk for text preprocessing (e.g., stopwords).

dataset
Spambase (UCI) – 4,601 email records with 57 numeric features.

SMS Spam Collection (UCI/Kaggle) – 5,574 SMS labeled ham/spam

SMS Model Accuracy: 97.49%
Email Model Accuracy: 96.81%
